{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "可悲的战斗人偶 第11章 EX1-1 寂寞的人偶",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行人因天色已晚而决定在草原上落脚。\\n马斯古拉在与大家一起吃饭的过程中\\n体会到了“和伙伴们一起吃饭才比较香”，\\n还在夜晚放哨时与卢卡的对话中\\n了解了自己曾感受到的“寂寞”。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呼……天快黑了。\\n今天就在这里休息吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "唉～肚子好饿呀～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "呵呵……那我们\\n赶快准备晚饭吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "晚饭……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "咦？话说，马斯古拉需要吃饭吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "需要。我们战斗人偶的能量\\n可以通过食物来补充。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "但是，我们可以转化为能量的东西\\n不仅限于人类的食物。\\n例如，这周围的花草也可以。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是吗？不过机会难得，\\n就跟我们一起吃同样的东西吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "诶……不，可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗯？我说了什么\\n奇怪的话吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "不，战场上经常军粮不足，\\n所以我们战斗人偶往往\\n不能和人类吃同样的东西……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "啥？怎么能这样。\\n过去的小气鬼可真多啊～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "但这的确是很现实的判断。\\n毕竟跟人类相比，\\n我们能摄取能量的东西更多。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "即便如此，\\n却硬要和人类吃一样的东西，\\n这样很没有效率。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "会说这样的话的家伙，\\n一定不知道和伙伴们\\n一起吃饭才比较香！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马斯古拉，\\n跟我们一起吃饭吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "卢卡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "来，请吧，马斯古拉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "十分感谢。\\n那我就不客气了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "呼～能在战场上\\n吃到这么香的饭\\n都是多亏了库菈乌啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "就是就是！\\n多亏有库菈乌在～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "突、突然间\\n你们这是怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "只是把平日的想法\\n说出来了而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "是啊是啊，重要的事\\n得好好说出来才行呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊，是这么回事啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "听你们夸奖我，我很高兴，\\n但饭只能一人一碗哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂喂，竟然认为我在\\n打这种小算盘。我明明只是\\n在感叹库菈乌劳苦功高……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "哎呀，是吗。那多出来的饭\\n我可要分给其他人了哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "怎么能这样，库菈乌！\\n这完全是两码事吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "啊哈哈哈……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马斯古拉？你在发什么呆啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "啊，难道……\\n不合你的口味吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "不，并不是这样，\\n应该说……我们战斗人偶\\n并没有“味觉”这种功能。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "诶！？\\n是说吃什么都不觉得香吗？\\n感觉有点可怜啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是吗……这样的话，\\n宝贵的吃饭时间也不会快乐啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "的确，至今为止\\n我都不曾从快不快乐的角度\\n思考过补充能量这件事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "但是……\\n你说得对，卢卡。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶？我说什么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "你说“和伙伴们一起吃饭\\n才比较香”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "和大家一起吃饭很快乐。\\n对于本应感受不到的“味道”，\\n我似乎也有所理解了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "现在我所感受到的，\\n应该就是“香”吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "谢谢大家。我还是第一次\\n感受到如此快乐的时光。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗨，马斯古拉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "卢卡？怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "没什么，就是想来陪陪你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "嗯？夜晚放哨的事不用担心。\\n周围没有帝国兵的踪影。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "索敌模式下，\\n我一个人能监视很广的范围。\\n你就放心休息吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我们战斗人偶并不会\\n感到疲劳，但我听说\\n人类是需要适当休息的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊，确实需要适当休息。\\n这一点，你也一样吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "诶？所以说，我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "总感觉不会疲劳\\n和不用休息是两回事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我觉得你也\\n休息一下比较好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "卢卡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "谢谢你……\\n不过，我没有睡眠这种功能，\\n就算休息也不知道该干什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唔……那就，\\n来和我聊聊天吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "聊、聊天……吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊，一个人守一整晚，\\n又无聊又寂寞吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "寂寞……寂寞……是吗……\\n啊，原来是这样啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "我有时会有种难以形容的感觉，\\n好像少了点什么，\\n又好像忘了些什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "原来这种感觉……\\n就是“寂寞”啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "原来我一直……都觉得寂寞啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马斯古拉……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那今后你就不会寂寞啦！\\n因为有我在！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "驱散寂寞最好的方法，\\n就是跟哥们胡闹一场！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_11_05_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120135_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "马斯古拉",
            "context": "哥、哥们……朋友……\\n卢卡是我的……朋友。",
